        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(doctor): preserve codex context metadata",
        "body": "Fixes #90448.\n\n## What changed\n\n- Preserves legacy `openai-codex` model context metadata when the canonical `openai` provider already exists.\n- Copies legacy model entries into `models.providers.openai.models` when the canonical provider has no matching model.\n- Merges missing `contextWindow`, `contextTokens`, and `maxTokens` fields into matching canonical model entries without overwriting explicit canonical values.\n- Adds regression coverage for empty canonical `openai.models`, matching canonical models with missing metadata, and matching canonical models with explicit metadata.\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\nSetup:\n\n- Repository: OpenClaw checkout.\n- Branch under test: `fastino-90448-codex-context-fallback`.\n- Proof script imports the real `src/commands/doctor/shared/legacy-config-migrate.ts` migration entrypoint from each checkout and runs it against a config with canonical `openai.models: []` plus legacy `openai-codex` `gpt-5.5` metadata.\n\nBefore, on current main:\n\n```text\nnode_modules/.bin/tsx /private/tmp/openclaw-90448-proof.ts /Users/allahyar/Documents/fastino-tasks/openclaw\n[]\n[\n  \"Removed models.providers.openai-codex because models.providers.openai already exists.\"\n]\n```\n\nAfter, on this branch:\n\n```text\nnode_modules/.bin/tsx /private/tmp/openclaw-90448-proof.ts /Users/allahyar/Documents/fastino-tasks/openclaw-tui-90448b\n[\n  {\n    \"id\": \"gpt-5.5\",\n    \"name\": \"GPT-5.5\",\n    \"contextTokens\": 272000,\n    \"maxTokens\": 16384,\n    \"reasoning\": false,\n    \"input\": [\n      \"text\"\n    ],\n    \"cost\": {\n      \"input\": 0,\n      \"output\": 0,\n      \"cacheRead\": 0,\n      \"cacheWrite\": 0\n    },\n    \"contextWindow\": 200000,\n    \"api\": \"openai-chatgpt-responses\"\n  }\n]\n[\n  \"Copied models.providers.openai-codex.models[].gpt-5.5 → models.providers.openai.models[].gpt-5.5.\",\n  \"Removed models.providers.openai-codex because models.providers.openai already exists.\"\n]\n```\n\n## Verification\n\n```text\ngit diff --check -- src/commands/doctor/shared/legacy-config-migrations.runtime.models.ts src/commands/doctor/shared/legacy-config-migrate.test.ts\n```\n\nNo output.\n\n```text\nnode scripts/test-projects.mjs src/commands/doctor/shared/legacy-config-migrate.test.ts\n\n[test] starting test/vitest/vitest.unit-fast.config.ts\n\n RUN  v4.1.7 /Users/allahyar/Documents/fastino-tasks/openclaw-tui-90448b\n\n Test Files  1 passed (1)\n      Tests  104 passed (104)\n   Start at  02:55:17\n   Duration  4.50s (transform 280ms, setup 0ms, import 777ms, tests 3.67s, environment 0ms)\n\n[test] passed 1 Vitest shard in 7.45s\n```\n\n## Platforms tested\n\n- macOS local checkout with Node 26 and repository test runner.\n\n## Limitations\n\n- This validates the doctor migration path directly; it does not run a full installed `openclaw doctor --fix` command.\n",
